Taken from Example and Test Vector for the ChaCha20 Cipher of https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8439#section-2.4.2

To test yourself here is the key, nonce, and counter below.

uint8_t key[32] = {0x00, 0x01, 0x02, 0x03, 0x04, 0x05, 0x06, 0x07,
                       0x08, 0x09, 0x0a, 0x0b, 0x0c, 0x0d, 0x0e, 0x0f, 0x10, 0x11,
                       0x12, 0x13, 0x14, 0x15, 0x16, 0x17, 0x18, 0x19, 0x1a, 0x1b,
                       0x1c, 0x1d, 0x1e, 0x1f};

uint8_t nonce[12] = {0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00};
    
uint32_t counter = 1;
